description: 2013.3.6  世界上最荒謬的抗議活動  [非法]繁殖業者聚集立法院..抗議動保法修法 一再的誤導合法業者跟飼主 甚至對支持法案的立委跟藝人人身攻擊  全部都只因為修法擋了他們的財路.. 這些非法繁殖業者..長年來製造多少流浪狗 殘殺多少生命.. 居然還敢說自己是愛狗的...  天底下最好笑的笑話... 我知道當天有不少是被誤導來出席的... 請不要再被他們騙上船了!  非法繁殖業者非常難抓.... 從來都只看的到被他們利用殆盡丟棄在路邊跟收容所的悽慘狗兒  今天居然全部自己跳出來...說自己愛狗... 好特別的愛狗方式啊!!!!!! 這種要命的愛..不要也罷啊..  以下對修法的解說請廣傳  根據《動保法》修正草案所列，第22條修正案：第3項修正為：「第一項業者以外之特定寵物飼主應為寵物絕育，但飼主向直轄市、縣(市)主管機關申報並提出繁殖管理說明後得免絕育，如有繁殖需求亦應申報，並在寵物出生後依第19條規定，植入晶片，辦理寵物登記。」增列第4項：「直轄市、縣(市)主管機關得要求前項申報飼主提供特定寵物飼養現況及受轉讓飼主資料。」  動保法27條正案增列第9款：「違反第22條第3項規定，經勸導改善仍未申報或為寵物絕育。」  因此，不結紮或是有繁殖需求是可以的，只要申請登記，並非「全面強制結紮」。   看到有的飼主對於結紮以後想生育裝不回去的說法...在此做個補充  想結紮的人..就會去把狗結紮..沒這法條也會去結紮..自然不會考慮未來想生育不能生育的問題 不想結紮..也不代表就是因為想生育..可能不想花錢或是不想給狗狗動手術 同為飼主我可以理解...我之前也不想給狗結紮,直到他睪丸發炎=_=  如果不想結紮...就去做登記...不管你要不要繁殖或是生育都沒關係 這還是關乎飼主的意願... 只是多了強制登記 可以管制萬一你生產了之後棄養或是非法販賣的行為  對於飼主而言.. 想結紮的飼主..想必就會去結紮...也不可能認為現在結紮多年後還要讓狗狗生 不想結紮的飼主..不管是因為想以後可能想讓狗生 或是不想給狗動手術都沒有關係 去登記告知不想結紮...就好 即使以後追蹤知道你沒結紮也沒生育...也沒有關係..... 所以並不會影響到飼主想不想結紮的權益...  那些非法繁殖業者不敢登記 是因為他們是非法販售..... 負責任的飼主...只是多個登記的動作 就跟打晶片一樣....是有多難?????  不要再被非法繁殖業者矇騙了..

transcript: Per què l'espoly fiscal, que ve deixa el nostre país, és de més de 7,000 milions d'euros. title: Salí / Canal 20 / 12.07.13 / BJ Sala / Parte 2
description: Camila Cibils conversa con Ariel Miguez, uno de los dueños de BJ Sala, que reabrió sus puertas este mes. Ubicado en pleno centro de Montevideo, sobre la calle Uruguay en la intersección de Río Branco, cuenta con un escenario profesionalmente equipado de audio y luces con todo el material imprescindible para los artistas, el público asistente y quienes forman parte del equipo de producción de cada evento. Además, en Salí, Camila charla con Rosana Demarco, curadora de la muestra Zoom, que actualmente puede visitarse en el CCE. ¿Qué hay detrás de un objeto, de una tipografía, de un espacio, de un estuche o de un marcapasos?, ¿cómo se genera el mobiliario que usamos diariamente? ¿Y el automóvil que nos transporta o el abrigo que nos envuelve? Zoom hace visible y pone en evidencia el proceso de diseño de once estudios de Diseño de Uruguay. Cerramos el programa escuchando la música de Martina Gadea, con su último videoclip Peter Pan. ¡Muchas propuestas para que no dejes de salir!  www.canal20.com.uy www.facebook.com/CanalVeinteUY @Canal20tv

title: Reforma no costará "ni un euro al contribuyente"
description: La vicepresidenta y portavoz del Gobierno, Soraya Sáenz de Santamaría, ha asegurado que la tercera reforma financiera que ha aprobado este viernes el Gobierno culmina la reestructuración del sector y se hace con un objetivo "básico y fundamental: que no cueste ni un euro al contribuyente".
hashtags: Consejo de Ministros, Europa Press, Internet, telediario, agencia de noticias, news, actualidad, noticias, Sáenz de Santamaría, Política, reforma financiera
transcript: Norma, por tanto, muy completa, una norma estructurada en, como verán, en los macarismos de solución de las crisis bancarias, en la mayor independencia, la actividad del banco de España, en una regulación completa del froc, se crea sí mismo como explicará el ministro de la sociedad de gestión de activos y se establecen nuevos macarismos de protección de los inversores. Con esta norma cumplimos además nuestros compromisos europeos y se hace en tiempo y forma de acuerdo con el memorando entendimiento, esta norma será además publicada inmediatamente. Complimos compromisos europeos en este ámbito y en otros sus que el alabor del gobierno está siendo muy intensa en estas fechas, como bien saben, esta semana al presidente del gobierno se ha reunido con el presidente con los golope después con el puse ante la República Francesa para impulsar, mecanismos como el año fiscal y la unión mancable. Estas semanas se reúnecó la cantidad de manacos, la señora Merkel, en este impulso, las medidas que en el ámbito de la unión de dopea permitan recuperación para meter a sea de la decisión, mejor y mayor cooperación, entre las economías, española y el enmaná en beneficio de ambos estados. Por tanto, y voy a dar la palabra al ministro de conemé competitividad, hoy traemos la culminación de uno de los elementos fundamentales básicos para lograrsele a la crisis coles, la restructura de este sistema financiero una norma completa para la resolución de las crisis bancarias y la protección de los inversores. Y se hace además con un objetivo termino con este colofón porque es de los más importantes, que no cuesta un euro al contribuyente, que sea una reforma que aprovechando la ayuda financiera obtenida de la Unión Europea, pueda y al largo del proceso establez en garantías para ello salventarse sin coste para el contribuyente.

transcript: I'm an adult, I have a car and a mortgage, but it's always fun when a game makes you feel like a kid again. Take spell tower, for example. It's as simple as the children's game, so a difting and challenging that you'll have a hard time putting it down. The object is the link words together from tiles that touch, an old fashioned word search, but you aren't limited to one direction, for example, you can link four letters that and all touch diagonally, horizontally, and reverse diagonally to make a word. You can then test that against four different modes, including a leisurely tower mode, and a time trial rush mode, which feel like totally different games. There are really more, more, more, more, more. Sorry. There's really no rush, quite like finding the word parsimity in the last few seconds, to beat your personal best, or the score of a friend, like that no-it-all Steve. Since spell tower plugs most specific scores to game center, comparing yourself to friends is super easy. We can all agree that Steve's a dick, right? Bottom line, game looks plain and classic, where nerds 11 and it's easy enough for a 6-year-old girl to learn. But, tough enough to frustrate, you have a loving hell out of a man, and he's been 30s like me. I'm sorry, it's too much. Steve, you've so glad you called. Anyhow, see you later.

title: UN Foundation Board Meeting in Norway: New African Connections Conference Part 2
description: In June 2011, twelve of the world's leading voices for global progress and change gathered for the UN Foundation Board of Directors meeting in Norway. The semi-annual meeting, presided over by UN Foundation Founder and Chairman Ted Turner, took place June 19-25 in Oslo and the northernmost regions of the country.  The Board met with government, corporate and nonprofit leaders to build support for UN efforts to improve global health, catalyze innovations in international development and call for global action on climate change. The meetings were hosted by Board member Gro Harlem Brundtland, Director-General Emeritus, World Health Organization and Former Prime Minister of Norway. The Board's discussions focused on ways to help new partners connect with the lifesaving work of the United Nations.

transcript: Now, it's my great pleasure to turn over the program to our colleagues at the UN Foundation for a really great series of announcements about some of the initiatives that will help to drive innovation forward in the very near future. So if I could ask Susan Myers to join us on stage from the UN Foundation, let's give her a round of applause. Well, thank you, Dan, and thanks all of you for being here. My name is Susan Meyers, I'm the Vice President of UN Relations at the UN Foundation. So as you can tell, I spend a lot of time thinking about the UN, which is one of the reasons that I'm so happy to be here in Norway with our Board of Directors, where we've had a great couple of days talking with people about the UN, about all the ways that Norway is working with the UN and how we can really deepen our partnerships there. You heard from some of our board members yesterday, I hope you've had a chance to meet some of my colleagues that have been here all day, Kate Dodson, who's our director of Global Health Integration, Leslie Cortes, who's been instrumental in starting up the Alliance for Clean Cook Stows, and you just heard a presentation about why that issue is so important. And Jennifer Pots with our M Health Alliance, who I'm going to call up to the stage momentarily to talk about an initiative that's happening with the M Health Alliance. But I just wanted to say the reason our board is here and the reason why we have so many staff here is not only because of our strong commitment to global health, but because we have also stepped up to what I share and called the SG's called Action on the Global Strategy for Women and Children's Health and you see that we put up this banner here every woman every child which represents what is becoming a truly global energetic effort in response to the Secretary General's leadership. So in addition to all of the ways the UN Foundation was working on global health issues and harnessing what we can do at our organization to respond to that call to action. We've also taken on a role as part of our support for the UN and being a platform connect for connecting people, idea, and resources to the UN to encourage others to get involved in support of the Secretary-General's leadership. So I have the exciting job today of calling some others up to this stage so you can hear what they're doing in response to this new initiative. Makes him "Freedom Fighter-ish" with his supers,specials,and he's got decent backstory. B+.    (Is there any story to this?)    Duke and Chaos soon found Dr. Pax somewhere in the forbidden section. Duke didn't listen to the warning,and well... Here he and his doofy sidekick Chaos are.    Chaos: "That's him! That's Dr.-"    *bang*    "WHAT ARE YOU DOING? YOU JUST SHOT AT HIM!!"    Duke: "He's one of them. He must die."    Chaos: "Dr. Pax was recruited against his will by Metroker! Please!!! He's a good man!!!"    Duke: "That's for me to know and you find out."    Pax: "Enough. If you have business with me,we can take this outside."    Duke: "Good enough for me doc. Now it's time to have a taste of your own medicine."    Pax took his coat off. Underneath it was a war torn man. Half man,half machine.    Chaos: "Slaughtered by Metroker's ungodly army,they tried turning him into a chimera.... They didn't succeed,and ended up destroying half his body..... He had to build a machine type body for himself to cover his burned out side...."    *ring ring*    Mario: "Duke,under NO circumstances is Pax allowed to die. Get him out of there!"    Duke: "I don't think the doc's on good terms with me now."    Mario: "Drag him and Chaos out of there by force!! Metroker must NOT be allowed to keep them!!"    Duke: "Got it." title: Novosadski maturanti u Skupštini grada
description: Novosadski maturanti gimnazije "Laza kostić" i srednje mašinske škole posetili su danas skupštinu grada.
hashtags: novi sad, laza kostić, skupština grada, maturanti
transcript: Na životnim prekretnici, maturanti sujmili priliku, da se boju pozniju se radom i situcij o koju uču školi. Po rodu poznava nje sapite njima kojima se babi lokalna se mopreva, preciingskubši njega da smatr da i učni kiva ajžnom pozniti i salokalom politikom. Lokanom politika je nešto, što možna pripoga nije zanimila, što se ti přes vakoreno funkcionanisanja svakčik život. Tako je prevoz, kako je vodu od kanalizacija, a kako je centrongrenije, nači, kako funkcionanije, še zalenimo i tako je nači, to je ono štos uštnijski i ksini onaj život nemi. Svači, načo ono mladka vi zaćite, no ulicu doksnaj vredite naši pući, to je slokama politik. Da se ovakim vidom, pove zivanje školzke teorije sa praksu najbolje leči, a politiczno skudučenika reko nam je je njiho profesor. Da zaastupljeno i tako jedno prednete kao šti ustajiv travo graćo na koja bestoju igina zjavštik tipa. Ismi da treve da i praktišno da svoj smisao onoga trenutka kacepoju jer imo na vako jedno mesćo. Naravno, pitalih smo šta ovoj posit imisle i sami jac. Prostore, kto je da smo doštio skupštimo grade, da je ćemo poznatih varnje ljudu donom saduje. ćemo je ti pili kupostimo, možda da kupitani, koja na sintero svoju. Pada sa obrez je mupolijtejčki baranaj kina, ćemo da vijemo, kako funkijani še razko upštimo. Potu će da ću pijsati pravni fakultet, verovatno ćemo povo znaciti.

title: Home Care Caldwell NJ: Medicare or Health Insurance pay for in-home care?
description: http://www.inhomecarecaldwell.com, 277 Fairfield Road, Fairfield, NJ 07004, (973) 244-9400
transcript: Does Medicare or health insurance pay for in-home care? Medicare and traditional health insurance only pays for skilled care. This means that the care must be ordered by a physician, must be medically necessary, and must be monitored by a health care professional. In the case of Medicare, the patient must also be homebound and unable to run errands or engage in activities outside of the home. Medicare and traditional health insurance pays for very limited amounts of care for very brief periods of time. and non-medical home care are typically not paid for by Medicare or traditional health insurance.

transcript: Apesar disso, houve descreta a melhor a na avaliação sobre a situação atual e da equilíbrio Bom dia, começa a agora mais uma edição do boletinho de abertura de mercados do último instante, a confiança do consumidor mida pela fundação de atulho Vargas caiu 0,4% em maio para 103,4 pontos. Apesar disso, houve descreta a melhor a na avaliação sobre a situação atual e da economia. Em May, o índice de satisfação atual subiu 0,9%. Também, nessa sexta-feira, a inflação semanalme de da PLCS subiu em 5 da sete captas pesquisadas. Na terceira semana do mês, o destaque de alta ficou com um porto alegre, onde o índice subiu 0,41%. Já em Salvador, o indicador registrou deflação 0,30%. Na cena internacional, as bolsas na Ásense rara um acessão cêndireção única, com os investidores de gerindo a piora nas perspectivas econômicas da China. O destaque do dia mais uma vez ficou com a Bolsa do Japão. Hoje, o índice Niquei 2021, da Bolsa de Toque, em Serraus Negócios, com alta de 0,89%, após forte e volatilidade. No vale o continente das Bolsa's locais, eu pera um embaixa, apesar dos bons indicadores econômicos divulgados pela Alemanha. No primeiro trimestre, a economia do país cresceu o 0,1%. De alclima de negócios alemão, avançou para 105,7 pontos. Os Estados Unidos usam em oostrute e iniciam os negócios em queda, apesar da melhora no número de pedidos à indústria, em abril o indicador avançou o 3,3%. description: Vidio dalam rangka pengecoran kubah utama Masjid Baitul Muttaqin Tunjungrejo pada tanggal 26-09-2010.  Pengerjaan pengecoran dilakukan oleh para relawan dari dalam desa dan luar desa Tunjungrejo.  Bersama ini pula masuk sumbangan langsung dari Bp. Parmo 1 sak seme, 20 sak semen dari Hamba Allah yg tidak mau di sebut namanya, 5 sak semen dari Hamba Allah, 20 sak semen juga dari Hamba Allah, lau 4 slop rokok sukun putih, juga snack, nasi bungkus, kopi, dll.  Dokumentasi untuk: http://masjidbaitulmuttaqintunjungrejo.blogspot.com/
hashtags: Hamba Allah, pengecoran fiesta, desa, dokumentasi, renovasi, masjid

transcript: You say you will never forget where you were when you heard the news on September 11, 2001, neither will I. I was on the 110th floor in a smoke-filled room with a man who called his wife to say goodbye. I held his finger steady as he dialed, I gave him peace to say, honey, I'm not going to make it, but it's okay, I'm ready to go. I was with his wife when he called as she fed breakfast to their children. I held her up as she tried to understand his words, and as she realized he wasn't coming home that night. I was in the stairwell of the 23rd floor when a woman cried out to me for help. I said I have been knocking on the door of your heart for 50 years. Of course I will show you the way home, only believe in me now. I was at the base of the building with the priest, ministering to the injured and devastated souls. I took him home to Tendez, Flockenhaven. He heard my voice and answered. I was on all four of those planes in every seat with every prayer. I was with the crews they were overtaken. I was in the very heart of the believers there, comforting and assuring them that their faith has saved them. I was in Texas, Kansas, London. I was standing next to you when you heard the terrible news. Did you sense me? I want you to know that I saw every face, I knew every name, though not all knew me. Some met me for the first time on the 86th floor. Some sought me with their last breath. Some couldn't hear me calling to them through the smoke and flames. Come to me, this way, take my hand. Some chose for the final time to ignore me. I did not place you in the tower that day, you may not know why, but I do. If you were there in that explosive moment in time, would you have reached for me? September 11, 2001 was not the end of the journey for you, but someday your journey will end. And I will be there for you as well, seek me now while I may be found, then at any moment you know you are ready to go. I will be in the stairwell of the final moment. Remember, I love you.

title: Humberto Tan in Congo (deel 1)
description: Reportage van het Nederlandse Rode Kruis in samenwerking met Humberto Tan om het thema tracing onder de aandacht te brengen. Geld geven aan het Rode Kruis? Kijk op www.rodekruis.nl
hashtags: Tan, Non-profit, Red, Rode, Cross, Ondersteuning, Humberto, Aperitivo, Opsporing, Kruis, Ontwikkelingshulp, Tracing
transcript: Het roodercruis helpt veertwijt mensen in nood, ze zijn als eerste aanwezig bij een rand, om levens te redden, maar ook om slachtovers op te vangen en te zorgen voor schoon drinkwater, voedsel en medicijnen. Het roodercruis helpt direct, veertwijt en al jaren lang. Ze zijn onderdeel van het grootste onafhankelijke hylpnetwerk ter wereld, die zowel in het buitenland als in Nederland hylpiet-amenten die dat het hartst nodig hebben. Ongeacht geloof nationaliteit of ras. Vrijwilligers spelen een centraal rol binnen het rode kruis en weel het wijt zijn er 108 miljoen vrijwilligers actief, die zich met hart en ziel inzetten. Naast vrijwilligers zijn ook Donateurs van onschatbare waarden. Alleen met uw financiërenstun zijn zei in staat om altijd en overal als eerste aanwezig te zijn. Zit op de grensens Bordondier, Rwanda en Congo, een aflopje jaar heeft hier een ovolig gevoerd, het de meeste 5 miljoen doden. Mijn niet alleen doden, als ze nog slacht of als die zei voor spruit of de hele land heb om te flugden. En de voornames te klachten of ze daarvan zijn kinderen. De dees special aflevering van appartievoel richten wij ons om de kinderen. Want het dode kruis proberen die kinderen weer te herenigen met de familie.

description: 蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen 如果我們不去想其他辦法增加電力供給，台灣將一直倚賴核能發電，畢竟辦法是人想出來的，事情是人在做，如果不動腦筋、事情就不會發生，而「養水種電」計畫就是一項新的產業­、新的生活形態、新的經濟模式的開始。 台灣是世界第二大的太陽能電池、電板生產國，如果政府推動太陽能發電、擴大內需市場，外銷的產品品質將更好、也更具競爭力，對台灣來說是一個極佳的產業發展機會；在發展在­地經濟產業的同時，也創造更多就業機會，這正是台灣目前最需要的。  參訪屏東養水種電，蔡英文：非核家園，現在開始做 全文：http://www.iing.tw/2011/06/blog-post_562.html  蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen 一直以來所說的話都有記錄，只要仔細看就能知道我講過的話以及立場、態度都非常一致，如果馬總統看不懂，請他再看一遍。我們要找的是符合21世紀一個好的、有建設性的且新­的對中關係基礎，也要脫離過去的框架；國民黨老是認為對手政策跟他們不同就是不對的政策，總是停留在傳統思考觀念上的建構，一直用舊的方法在處理這些問題，這是不好的態度­，也只會讓事情越來越糟，國民黨有時候也應該跟對手學習。  對中關係立場始終一致，國民黨應脫離舊框架 全文：http://www.iing.tw/2011/06/blog-post_24.html

title: Reportagem TV Vanguarda -  Crime Ambiental
description: Reportagem sobre a Audiência pública organizada  pela Federação Pro Costa Atlântica em São Sebastião
transcript: Estão se bastão realizou uma audiência pública ao ontem para discutir a ocupação irregular em áreas de preservação ambiental na costa sul da cidade. Nossa equipe foi conferir de perto as denúncias e descobrir uma área devastada pela própria prefeitura. É difícil acreditar, mas essa é uma obra concluída na praia de campurinha em São Sebastião. O local era para estar assim uma área de preservação permanente, mas a prefeitura decidiu derrubar a mata nativa na imagem do rio para evitar enchentes na comunidade do areião, ocupação irregular desde a década de 90. Tiraram as árvores, tiraram o material do fundo, o Rio de Janeiro nas margens, ou seja, eles tiraram a electriverjetação, que a mar de preservação, que é mata-se aliário, eles ateraram as margens impedindo crescimentos de novas plantas, né? Esse crime ambiental foi revelado por meio de um apiamento aéreo que está sendo feito na costa sul de São Sebastião, a um ano e meio pela fundação pro Costa Atlântica, que reunispecialistas, moradores, comerciantes e empresários da região. O que é a susta, é que esse é só um dos problemas encontrados. Nesse mesmo local, o esgoto vai direto para o Rio Camburí, o listo está por todos os lados, e até o curso do Rio foi modificado nesse trecho na praia da barra dos saías imagens diantes e depois impressionam. Só nessa comunidade, seriam quase sem construções irregulares a mais em um anime. Enjo que ia onde denuncia que imóveis de luxo foram construídos com mais de 9 metros de altura, o que é proibido por lei. Que eu assumo para você que nós temos que fazer uma recuperação mais rápido possível da lida, aquela mata siliada, porque uma mata extremamente importante para aquela região. E agora os nossos trabalhos são nesse sentido tentar recuperar o que foi perdido ali. E sobre as construções irregulares, o prefeito da cidade disse que a fiscalização existe, As por conta da extensão da costa, que é 100 e 10 quilômetros, é difícil evitar esse tipo de regularidade. Ponto fundamental para um diretor. Em cima disso, nós estamos criando a opção dos bolções habitacionais ao longo do município para criar lotes populares, para que essa população tem a opção de ficar legalizada que fazer suas construções de acordo com a lei. Sobre as construções com mais de 9 metros de altura, o prefeito informou que depende de decisões judiciais para demolição desses imóveis.
